Everything Completed.

NOTE: JPG images are stored in {working-dir}/images

Program has two display options:
    1. Through OpenGl Window 
    2. Through a saved .bmp image file in the directory

To build: 
make
./rayT #

Argument List for #
1 - Scene 1
2 - Scene 2
3 - Scene 3
4 - Scene 4
5 - Renders All Scenes into .bmp files, displays the last scene in OpenGl